oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Masonic Building Collapse, 1949
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of the Masonic Building in downtown Clarksville in mid-collapse. Dust and debris flies through the air as the roof and brick walls crumble to the ground.
